<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="description" content="sbomify new user welcome notification">
        <meta name="keywords" content="sbomify, welcome, new user, notification">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Welcome to sbomify</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Welcome to sbomify!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for joining our platform. We're excited to have you on board.</p>
        <p>
            {% if user.first_name %}
                Hello {{ user.first_name }},
            {% else %}
                Hello {{ user.email }},
            {% endif %}
        </p>
        <p>We're excited to have you join the sbomify community. Your account has been successfully created.</p>
        <p>Feel free to reach out if you have any questions.</p>
        <p>
            Best regards,
            <br>
            The sbomify Team
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
